{"tid":2288574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google 引新集體訴訟，電話不使用下傳輸 260MB 數據","createTime":"2020-11-16T14:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T01:26:26.000Z","uid":1886,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4ceed22386208ea77e9be6c8a2c2695066c6b0","tid":2288574,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"Google 周四（12 日）被指控其通過未經批准以及未公開的傳輸方式竊取 Android 用戶的移動網絡數據，在後台向 Google 傳輸一些與用家無關的數據 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/16/google-hidden-transfers/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F16%2Fgoogle-hidden-transfers%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu5nDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=91fe04fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/16/google-hidden-transfers/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"04f8381152e592a97fa45f2942f0e2ff6955b9ca","tid":2288574,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:43:10.000Z","msg":"有用戶在美國聯邦地方法院對 Google 發起集體訴訟，指 Google 在未經用戶同意下，在後台使用 Android 用戶的移動網絡數據進行數據傳輸，利用 Android 用戶的移動網絡數據向 Google 提取和傳輸大量信息，而該些數據與用家無關。"},{"pid":"c6533be6c1e4166669830bb24eeff88eb4f86cc4","tid":2288574,"uid":155818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:43:43.000Z","msg":"Android <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070c1b46fced0f17531fbd39ae01a1009fe91aa5","tid":2288574,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"為了證實相關事件，原告律師使用全新的 Samsung Galaxy S7 進行測試，發現電話在閒置且沒有 Wi-Fi 連接的情況下，被發送並接收了 8.88MB 的數據，其中 94％的通信與 Google有關。測試可見，電話每小時會將數據傳輸至 Google 約 16 次，24 小時內約傳輸 389 次，就算手機沒有使用，每月更傳輸高達 260MB 數據資料。"},{"pid":"437a28e1eefa0873bad55c2e3fe7f8abd66a1506","tid":2288574,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"上訴者指出，Google 的服務條款、隱私政策、Google Play 託管協議，以及《 Google Play 服務條款》皆未有指出用戶需要承擔 Google 的傳輸，而即使相關傳輸仍必須，Apple 的 iPhone 傳輸數量亦只是 Google 的十分之一，故上訴者指控 Google 相關做法實屬過份。"},{"pid":"d2c314e60962931fab43affdff13d3dd125d6460","tid":2288574,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:44:32.000Z","msg":"上訴者投訴指控 Google 進行了這些未公開的數據傳輸，以進一步發展其廣告業務。現時 Google 未對訴訟的指控作出任何回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"6bd22385fa31a29fcb2cd520ff424ca5ea051b16","tid":2288574,"uid":1886,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBMBK6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBMBK6N.jpg&h=26bc2705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fce7e185cc3279fab5bbdf7a99074356ccb6f041","tid":2288574,"uid":81113,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:50:16.000Z","msg":"Android user:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WprOscV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWprOscV.gif&h=a246a3b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25f2972b48d887a06160716926e9c8fb0b544b49","tid":2288574,"uid":20914,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"慢慢大家就會發現其實而家係冇私隱可言<br />\n只係睇你想畀邊間公司"},{"pid":"3f00db40705881574a3c7566e7b922bcd3949885","tid":2288574,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25f2972b48d887a06160716926e9c8fb0b544b49","tid":2288574,"uid":20914,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"慢慢大家就會發現其實而家係冇私隱可言<br />\n只係睇你想畀邊間公司"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:08:14.000Z","msg":"你個腦正常啲就知道 數碼化嘅嘢 全部無所遁形"},{"pid":"a31d6af640ff776703e707b6511f4ca47f1e2c7b","tid":2288574,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im